Kerala - Grapqh API

Cet API porte sur Kerala, un Etat en Inde. Elle permet de consulter les hébergements, les attractions et les meilleures saisons pour visiter Kerala.

API Endpoints
https://fd-api-graphql.deta.dev/graphql

Queries

attractions

Response

Returns [Attraction!]!

Arguments
Name Description
where - AttractionWhere
options - AttractionOptions

Example

Query
query attractions(
  $where: AttractionWhere,
  $options: AttractionOptions
) {
  attractions(
    where: $where,
    options: $options
  ) {
    id
    name
    attractionsInPlace {
      ...PlaceFragment
    }
    attractionsInPlaceAggregate {
      ...AttractionPlaceAttractionsInPlaceAggregationSelectionFragment
    }
    attractionsInPlaceConnection {
      ...AttractionAttractionsInPlaceConnectionFragment
    }
  }
}
Variables
{
  "where": AttractionWhere,
  "options": AttractionOptions
}
Response
{
  "data": {
    "attractions": [
      {
        "id": "xyz789",
        "name": "xyz789",
        "attractionsInPlace": [Place],
        "attractionsInPlaceAggregate": AttractionPlaceAttractionsInPlaceAggregationSelection,
        "attractionsInPlaceConnection": AttractionAttractionsInPlaceConnection
      }
    ]
  }
}

    after: $after,
